{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/blog/2008-11-18-to-get-a-wife-you-need-to-rip-a-rib/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Lambdacurry"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"d483d221-7a1e-5bc5-b2b7-c64f8bb08870","excerpt":"[caption id=“attachment_179” align=“alignleft” width=“214” caption=“Charu and My invitation”][/caption] And that’s what I found out these past three years, ever…","html":"<p>[caption id=“attachment_179” align=“alignleft” width=“214” caption=“Charu and My invitation”]<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 750px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8dd8d3d204f1885373cd6ea4d8038332/acb04/charu-sandeeps-invitation.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 140%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Charu and My invitation\"\n        title=\"Charu and My invitation\"\n        src=\"/static/8dd8d3d204f1885373cd6ea4d8038332/acb04/charu-sandeeps-invitation.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8dd8d3d204f1885373cd6ea4d8038332/0479a/charu-sandeeps-invitation.jpg 250w,\n/static/8dd8d3d204f1885373cd6ea4d8038332/41099/charu-sandeeps-invitation.jpg 500w,\n/static/8dd8d3d204f1885373cd6ea4d8038332/acb04/charu-sandeeps-invitation.jpg 750w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>[/caption]</p>\n<p>And that’s what I found out these past three years, ever since that fateful day at the kickboxing gym. Was it very Christian of me, to adhere so strictly to the Book of Genesis? It sure did hurt …</p>\n<p>A wise man (or a seriously drunk one) once told me, ”<em>parents know a lot.. but they dont know everything</em>”. In this case, they sure did’nt - for not only do we not eat the same food, we dont speak the same native language. But, <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bollywood\">Bollywood</a> and <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rajnikanth\">Rajnikanth</a> unites all I’d say.</p>\n<p>Please wish me luck in doing the dishes, taking the garbage out and not getting wasted on weekends. It is sure going to be hard.</p>\n<p>Oh and the credit for the card goes to Charu, who used her enviable skills as a Copywriter to get it done and printed.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"To get a wife, you need to rip a rib","date":"November 18, 2008"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/2008-11-18-to-get-a-wife-you-need-to-rip-a-rib/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2008-10-23-antivirus-shootdown/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Antivirus shootdown"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2008-11-21-transmeta-and-the-ipod/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Transmeta and the Ipod"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2778469899","2841359383","2882394463","3616023293"]}